{"title":"登楼感怀","authors":["郑剑"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":5,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"登楼感怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春日向晚独登高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临窗沐风暂逍遥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天边烟霞藏旧梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下楼台锁心潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇事不苟多思量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为文求新细推敲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲寄疏狂随燕雀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翩翩飞入柳树梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝镰孤悬西天陲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜阑人静春风微。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修竹变幻吐清辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身增百尺悉绪少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神游万仞壮思飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世情物理古通今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"居高方解此中味。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}